00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:16,980
And it was so, and God made the beast of the earth

263
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:19,620
after his kind and cattle after their kind

264
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:22,860
and everything that creepeth upon the earth after his kind.

265
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:25,260
And God saw that it was good.

266
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:29,020
Look at the crowning moment, if you will, in verse 26.

267
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:33,060
And God said, let us make man in our image

268
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:35,740
after our likeness and let them have dominion

269
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:38,580
