339
00:16:07,420 --> 00:16:10,220
And we find this evening that as we study

340
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:12,940
Genesis chapter number one and we focus tonight

341
00:16:12,940 --> 00:16:16,100
on understanding these names of God

342
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:20,540
