00:19:19,059 --> 00:19:20,300
that was going on.

400
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:23,700
And basically, Rabshakka came delivering a message

401
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:26,220
from Sennacherib saying, we're gonna take you captive

402
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:29,620
as well, and he says something along these lines

403
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:32,860
and the way that I'll paraphrase it for you is this,

