433
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:10,640
Incline thine ear, O Lord, and hear.

434
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:13,760
Open thine eyes, O Lord, and see,

435
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:16,480
and hear all the words of Sennacherib,

436
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:20,240
