468
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:48,920
Oh, but my God is Elohim, he's the creator,

469
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:50,200
he's the strong one.

470
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:55,200
There's always hope because my God is the strong one.

471
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:59,320
And here, there's many names that he uses of God

472
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:01,520
